<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><!-- end .ru-story -->
<div class="ru-story">
<div class="w75 right"><img width="75" height="75" border="0" alt="Dewey &amp; LeBoeuf Leaders Cleared of Some Charges; Jury Deadlocked on Others" src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2015/10/14/business/14DB-DEWEYweb2/14DB-DEWEYweb2-square320.jpg"/></div>
